<h1>Tzatziki</h1>
<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
<li>1 cup Greek yogurt  </li>
<li>1/2 English cucumber, grated and squeezed dry  </li>
<li>1 tablespoon lemon juice  </li>
<li>1 tablespoon olive oil  </li>
<li>1 garlic clove, minced  </li>
<li>1 teaspoon dried dill</li>
<li>1/4 teaspoon salt  </li>
<li>1/4 teaspoon black pepper  </li>
</ul>
<h2>Steps</h2>
<ol>
<li>Mix together all ingredients in a bowl until fully combined.</li>
<li>Refrigerate for at least 15 minutes to let the flavors meld before serving.  </li>
</ol>
